// ============================================================
// JobNet.co.ke — Production Database Schema (Prisma + MySQL)
// ============================================================
// Covers all 8 prototypes + Job Seeker Dashboard + M-Pesa Payments
// + SEO + DPA Compliance + Analytics + CMS + Google Jobs
//
// Design Decisions:
//   - Enums enforced at DB level via Prisma enum types (v3 change)
//   - All enum values UPPER_SNAKE_CASE for consistency
//   - Location stored as structured fields (country, county, town) plus display string
//   - No JobCategory table (driven by hub-config.js / org_data.js)
//   - Json type for array fields (MySQL JSON columns)
//   - Nullable userId on orders (walk-in WhatsApp orders)
//   - Nullable userId on reactions (anonymous users via fingerprint)
//   - Partial payment support via paidAmount/balanceDue on orders
//   - Salary fields exist but optional (salaryMin, salaryMax, salaryCurrency, salaryPeriod)
//   - Opportunities linked to Company (optional FK)
//   - socialLinks JSON on Company for dynamic social media profiles
//
// v3 Changes (DB-Level Enums):
//   - All string-validated enums replaced with Prisma enum types
//   - MySQL ENUM columns enforce valid values at DB level
//   - CompanySize values: "1-10"→SIZE_1_10, "1000+"→SIZE_1000_PLUS
//   - Normalized lowercase enums to UPPER_SNAKE_CASE:
//     AuthProvider, OtpPurpose, ReactionType, NewsletterType, WhatsAppContext
//   - Shared enums: JobStatus (Job + Opportunity), EmploymentType (Job + JobAlert),
//     OrganizationIndustry (Company + Job)
//   - 29 enum types defined, 0 new tables
//
// v2 Changes (SEO + Google Jobs):
//   - Job: added publishedAt (CRITICAL for Google Jobs datePosted),
//     featuredImage, industry, viewCount, applicantCount, createdBy
//   - Opportunity: added featuredImage, createdBy;
//     removed: category (merged into opportunityType), provider, value, currency,
//     targetAudience, fieldOfInterest, source, sourceUrl, externalApplyUrl
//   - Company: added size (Google Jobs numberOfEmployees), createdBy (admin who created);
//     removed tagline, removed userId/user owner relation
//   - Education, skills, benefits, qualifications live in description
//     (structured via markdown template — Google parses headings + bullets)
// ============================================================

generator client {
  provider = "prisma-client-js"
}

datasource db {
  provider = "mysql"
  url      = env("DATABASE_URL")
}

// ============================================================
